text: Aqel Biltaji (10 February 1941 – 28 February 2021) was a Jordanian politician. He was Mayor of Amman from 8 September 2013 until 20 August 2017. Biltaji was born in Gaza, Egypt. Biltaji died of COVID-19 on 28 February 2021 in Amman, just two weeks after his 80th birthday.وفاة عقل بلتاجي.. والشواربة ينعاه ==References== Category:Mayors Category:Jordanian politicians Category:1941 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic
